@reub_selby and i have a locker bundle in @fortnite 👽 

you can get it now in the item shop 💰 
it includes Axo, neon backboard back bling, fresh fish pickaxe, prismatic edge wrap and vibin’ emote🚶🏻‍♂️❤️‍🔥

it’s only available for 48 hours so go and get it asap and make sure you always thank the bus driver 😵‍💫🙇🏼‍♀️🚌 

#fortniteinvasion #epicpartner

node.text:
We had the pleasure of hosting a dinner at Gymkhana on Monday evening to celebrate the launch of the company. We were joined by some of the most compelling and pivotal individuals, who are shaping the industry right now, and will continue to in the years to come. It was an unforgettable evening and marked the beginning of a very exciting journey for us at Rapt. Thank you to everyone who attended 🥂

@gymkhanalondon

Thank you @maisondemode for honouring me alongside @rosariodawson and @abrimaerwiah of @studiooneeightynine at this year’s Sustainable Style Awards. 

I could not be there in person but I still got to dress up in this beautifully sustainable @GabrielaHearst and @bethany_williams_london combo which made me feel 💥💥💥

Thank you to the many incredible activists across the fashion industry who are working tirelessly every day to impact change 🤍

#SustainableStyleAwards @cartier
